  "texts": [
    "However, these instructions often tend to be overly detailed and specific, which differ from real-world scenarios.",
    "After observing online user cases, we noticed that their proposed tasks are similar to the real user examples in Figure 1.",
    "Users tend to describe their current situation or the category of information they need, rarely mentioning the tools they require, let alone the API names.",
    "Intuitively, users do not care which specific APIs LLM uses to complete their tasks and are unlikely to remember the functions of massive APIs.",
    "For example, a ToolBench case like \"coordinates 39.5501°N, 105.7821°W\" is unlikely to occur in a real-world scenario."
  ],
